headline: Aon Announces Strategic Investment in eMed to Scale GLP-1 Population Health Platform
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, today announced a strategic investment in eMed Population Health, Inc., an emerging leader in the delivery of GLP-1 programs. The partnership will enhance employer sponsored access to GLP-1 therapies and scale solutions for obesity.

headline: MSIG USA Appoints Hank Kinne as Mountain/South Central States Region Distribution Leader
summary: MSIG USA, a leading provider of specialty commercial insurance, today announced the appointment of Hank Kinne as Mountain/South Central states region distribution leader. He will report to Joseph Fitzpatrick, head of distribution for MSIG USA.
